	<description>
		<![CDATA[
			<div class="overview-header">
			<h2>
			  <small style="display: block;">Responsive Joomla template for Designer Portfolio and corporate portfolio for both Joomla 2.5 and Joomla 3 - <strong>JA Sugite</strong>.</small>
			</h2>
			<p>Together with Parallax design and the clean look, <strong>JA Sugite</strong> is sure to impress just about anyone. This beautiful Joomla template supports the 
			favorite Joomla blogging component - EasyBlog, RTL language layout at default, Bootstrap 3 at core and stays stunning on all type of devices.</p>
			<p>Thanks to the T3 Framework, <strong>JA Sugite</strong> is highly compatible with numerous 3rd party Joomla templates. It has a 
			flexible layout structure, and is easy to customize with ThemeMagic or via Layout Configuration - the crazy cool features of 
			T3 Framework.</p>
			</div>
				]]>
	</description>
